<lb n="0930a17" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1193</head>
<lb n="0930a18" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0930001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】明本</note>妙吉祥平等瑜伽祕密觀身成佛
<lb n="0930a19" ed="T"/>儀軌</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0930a20" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0930a21" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">宋大契丹國師中天竺
<lb n="0930a22" ed="T"/>摩竭陀國三藏法師慈賢譯</byline>
<lb n="0930a23" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT20p0930a2301">凡欲課誦法事供養。先歸命佛念八大願。真
<lb n="0930a24" ed="T"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0930a25" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930a2501" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>沒騰達囉&CB00805;<note place="inline">二合</note>左<note place="inline">二</note>僧伽左<note place="inline">三</note>怛哩<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0930a26" ed="T"/>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00344;囉<note place="inline">二合四</note>麼努怛&CB03298;<note place="inline">二合五</note>母兔唧黨
<lb n="0930a27" ed="T"/><note place="inline">六</note>迦嚕弭也<note place="inline">二合</note>扇<note place="inline">上聲七</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;囉刺闥<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0930a28" ed="T"/>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>悉達曳<note place="inline">八</note>&CB00135;舍拏薩&CB00085;播波南<note place="inline">九</note>奔抳
<lb n="0930a29" ed="T"/>也<note place="inline">二合</note>喃左努謨那南<note place="inline">十</note>訖哩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00107;&CB00425;&CB00085;僧左
<pb n="0930b" id="T20.1193.0930b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0930b01" ed="T"/>哩舍也<note place="inline">二合</note>弭<note place="inline">十一</note>阿哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>瑟吒<note place="inline">二合下&CB00330;降切</note>&CB00344;播
<lb n="0930b02" ed="T"/>施達<note place="inline">十二</note>伊&CB00805;吠&CB00256;母播那野<note place="inline">十三</note>夜&CB00085;怛<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0930b03" ed="T"/>囉底也<note place="inline">二合</note>囉&CB00344;弭&CB00576;<note place="inline">十四</note>夜&CB00085;在薩素哩曳<note place="inline">十
<lb n="0930b04" ed="T"/>五</note>阿底養<note place="inline">二合</note>哆哩&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>抳&CB00085;馱<note place="inline">十六</note>&CB00425;囉
<lb n="0930b05" ed="T"/>寫賀囉喃<note place="inline">十七</note>阿沒&CB00772;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀左哩養<note place="inline">二合十八</note>怛那
<lb n="0930b06" ed="T"/>&CB00085;迦<note place="inline">二合</note>鼻努麼兔播惹那拏<note place="inline">十九</note>播拏尾迦&CB00256;
<lb n="0930b07" ed="T"/>薩拏<note place="inline">二十</note>麼&CB00256;&CB00085;囉那<note place="inline">二合</note>迦哩&CB00135;<note place="inline">二合</note>底耶<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0930b08" ed="T"/>儗怛&CB00085;&CB00135;多<note place="inline">二十一</note>阿&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>憾&CB00135;尾<note place="inline">二合</note>囉閉
<lb n="0930b09" ed="T"/>怛哩<note place="inline">二合</note>囉閉<note place="inline">引二十二</note></p>
<lb n="0930b10" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0930b1001"><l>初入道場</l><l>面向於佛</l><l>坐想此身</l>
<lb n="0930b11" ed="T"/><l>碎如微塵</l><l>返收攝身</l><l>如金剛體</l></lg>
<lb n="0930b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930b1201">真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0930b13" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930b1301" type="dharani">唵囉祖波&CB00344;哆薩囉&CB00085;達麼<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0930b14" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930b1401">口四業清淨。</p>
<lb n="0930b15" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930b1501" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;枳也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB02122;馱薩&CB00085;達囉麼<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;枳也<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0930b16" ed="T"/>合</note>&CB02122;度唅</p>
<lb n="0930b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930b1701">心三業清淨。</p>
<lb n="0930b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930b1801" type="dharani">唵唧哆&CB02122;馱薩&CB00085;囉摩<note place="inline">二合</note>唧哆&CB02122;度唅</p>
<lb n="0930b19" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930b1901">身三業清淨。</p>
<lb n="0930b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930b2001" type="dharani">娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆&CB00085;&CB02122;馱薩&CB00085;達囉麼<note place="inline">二合</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0930b21" ed="T"/>娑&CB00085;&CB02122;度唅</p>
<lb n="0930b22" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0930b2201"><l>三業清淨已</l><l>運心六道中</l>
<lb n="0930b23" ed="T"/><l>一切諸眾生</l></lg>
<lb n="0930b24" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930b2401">報障業障煩惱等障。悉皆消滅獲得清淨。次
<lb n="0930b25" ed="T"/>想上方佛壇運心供養。又想自手作金剛手。
<lb n="0930b26" ed="T"/>足眼心等亦復如是。以金剛身禮事諸佛。然
<lb n="0930b27" ed="T"/>後又想自手五指。取金剛智五甘露水自灌
<lb n="0930b28" ed="T"/>其頂。洗滌五身十業六塵。想凡夫身都無所
<lb n="0930b29" ed="T"/>有。如淨月輪輪上己身。吽字之形猶如光焰。
<pb n="0930c" id="T20.1193.0930c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0930c01" ed="T"/>依月輪住如燈光量念此真言加持七遍。真
<lb n="0930c02" ed="T"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0930c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930c0301" type="dharani">唵&CB00155;地唧多母怛跛<note place="inline">二合</note>那耶弭</p>
<lb n="0930c04" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930c0401">復想吽字形。月輪上而住。如大光明聚。想身
<lb n="0930c05" ed="T"/>火星散。良久而復收。真言七遍。</p>
<lb n="0930c06" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930c0601" type="dharani">唵素佉麼<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0930c07" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0930c0701"><l>復想月輪上</l><l>有小光明住</l>
<lb n="0930c08" ed="T"/><l>而誦此真言</l><l>應當一七遍</l></lg>
<lb n="0930c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930c0901">真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0930c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930c1001" type="dharani">唵底瑟吒<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0930c11" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0930c1101"><l>小光明不動</l><l>想身旋復去</l>
<lb n="0930c12" ed="T"/><l>而念此真言</l><l>亦應一七遍</l></lg>
<lb n="0930c13" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930c1301">真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0930c14" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930c1401" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>娑頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0930c15" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0930c1501"><l>復想身而來</l><l>念真言七遍</l></lg>
<lb n="0930c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930c1601">真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0930c17" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930c1701" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>僧賀囉&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0930c18" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0930c1801"><l>復想身而入</l><l>將成大覺身</l>
<lb n="0930c19" ed="T"/><l>念此祕密言</l><l>加持一七遍</l></lg>
<lb n="0930c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930c2001">真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0930c21" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930c2101" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>尾捨吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0930c22" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0930c2201"><l>想小光明住</l><l>如同大覺身</l>
<lb n="0930c23" ed="T"/><l>誦此陀羅尼</l><l>復應一七遍</l></lg>
<lb n="0930c24" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930c2401">真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0930c25" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930c2501" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>怛麼句唅</p>
<lb n="0930c26" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0930c2601"><l>又復觀自身</l><l>為金剛之體</l>
<lb n="0930c27" ed="T"/><l>猶如如來身</l><l>等同無有異</l>
<lb n="0930c28" ed="T"/><l>三誦此真言</l></lg>
<lb n="0930c29" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0930c2901" type="dharani">唵野多薩&CB00085;怛他&CB00344;哆娑怛<note place="inline">二合</note>佉憾</p>
<pb n="0931a" id="T20.1193.0931a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0931a01" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0931a0101">次應右手執金剛杵。左手執鈴作波羅蜜。菩
<lb n="0931a02" ed="T"/>薩持課杵表佛印。其杵五鈷表如來。鈴表四
<lb n="0931a03" ed="T"/>波羅蜜。菩薩諦想自身作寶生佛。擲杵三遍。
<lb n="0931a04" ed="T"/>次當舞轉作蓮華印。印已頂禮。禮已執杵。指
<lb n="0931a05" ed="T"/>頂口心。誦唵阿<note place="inline">去聲</note>吽。三種智字。想頂作壇。
<lb n="0931a06" ed="T"/>先想安置頂內蓮華。其蓮八葉。安蓮華已。次
<lb n="0931a07" ed="T"/>臥金剛。其金剛上有日月輪。於日輪上有十
<lb n="0931a08" ed="T"/>二字。月輪之上復有十六。梵字之母。出生之
<lb n="0931a09" ed="T"/>法。不可得故。於月輪上想安唵字。又觀唵字
<lb n="0931a10" ed="T"/>旋復而去。良久乃來作輪字形。復想一返為
<lb n="0931a11" ed="T"/>毘盧佛。餘四方佛次第安置。悉皆同等四波
<lb n="0931a12" ed="T"/>羅蜜。應念種智而居四隅坐三重座。無其月
<lb n="0931a13" ed="T"/>輪。下至明王。應皆如是。已上九位住第一院。
<lb n="0931a14" ed="T"/>內八菩薩念種智字。於第二院次第分布。外
<lb n="0931a15" ed="T"/>十二尊十明王等。亦念種智及其密號。處第
<lb n="0931a16" ed="T"/>三院依位安立。想壇畢已。觀身為佛。即念佛
<lb n="0931a17" ed="T"/>壇。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0931a18" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0931a1801" type="dharani">沒馱&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>達囉室哩<note place="inline">二合</note>滿曩<note place="inline">一</note>底哩<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0931a19" ed="T"/>合</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合二</note>鼻&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>婆尾曩<note place="inline">三</note>阿底瑟吒
<lb n="0931a20" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>曩播能<note place="inline">上聲</note>弭&CB00135;養<note place="inline">二合四</note>迦嚕凍迦野&CB00085;日
<lb n="0931a21" ed="T"/>哩<note place="inline">二合</note>曩<note place="inline">五</note>那舍捺儗<note place="inline">二合</note>僧悉體<note place="inline">二合</note>哆沒馱
<lb n="0931a22" ed="T"/><note place="inline">六</note>屈嘌<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00680;&CB00418;<note place="inline">七</note>迦野&CB00085;日哩<note place="inline">二合</note>曩<note place="inline">引八</note>唵
<lb n="0931a23" ed="T"/>薩&CB00085;怛他&CB00344;哆<note place="inline">九</note>迦野&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合十</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>娑
<lb n="0931a24" ed="T"/>&CB00085;怛麼句唅<note place="inline">十一</note></p>
<lb n="0931a25" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0931a2501">次想口中法壇位。想阿字形。去而復來成寶
<lb n="0931a26" ed="T"/>蓮華。復想一返為阿彌陀。同前觀想。應念法
<lb n="0931a27" ed="T"/>壇。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0931a28" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0931a2801" type="dharani">達囉麼<note place="inline">二合</note>吠&CB00085;迦播他室哩<note place="inline">二合</note>滿曩<note place="inline">一</note>底哩
<lb n="0931a29" ed="T"/>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>鼻&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>婆尾曩<note place="inline">二</note>阿地瑟吒<note place="inline">二
<pb n="0931b" id="T20.1193.0931b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0931b01" ed="T"/>合</note>娜播能弭&CB00135;養<note place="inline">二合三</note>迦嚕凍&CB00085;&CB00344;&CB00085;日哩<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0931b02" ed="T"/>娜<note place="inline">四</note>那舍捺儗<note place="inline">二合</note>僧悉帝<note place="inline">二合</note>哆沒馱<note place="inline">五</note>屈嘌
<lb n="0931b03" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00680;&CB00418;<note place="inline">六</note>&CB00085;&CB00344;&CB00085;日哩<note place="inline">二合</note>曩<note place="inline">引七</note>唵薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">八</note>
<lb n="0931b04" ed="T"/>怛他&CB00344;多<note place="inline">九</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合十</note>婆&CB00085;怛麼<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0931b05" ed="T"/>合</note>句憾<note place="inline">十一</note></p>
<lb n="0931b06" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0931b0601">次想心內僧壇位。觀吽字形。去而復來即為
<lb n="0931b07" ed="T"/>金剛。想一返成阿&CB00434;尊。同前觀行。當念僧壇。
<lb n="0931b08" ed="T"/>陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0931b09" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0931b0901" type="dharani">唧哆&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>達囉室哩<note place="inline">二合</note>滿曩<note place="inline">一</note>底哩<note place="inline">二
